br />\n簽完張約就同佢講我地唔承認張約<br />\n<br />\n睇佢制唔制<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講得出呢d野嘅人個腦都有問題"},{"pid":"fd640b02ad214e9f2428acc7679baf762c4851eb","tid":642791,"uid":142888,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"台灣就係一直爭議緊 ，究竟日本殖民管治時期嗰陣應該叫 日治時期 定 日佔時期 好，台灣大中華膠同國民黨傾向叫日佔時期，所以有好多爭議<br />\n<br />\n香港一直都唔在乎呢啲事，就連3年06個月嗰陣 都叫日治時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過睇嚟香港好快就進入台灣呢啲爭議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲啲TVB都會開始叫英佔時期，仲要幫香港旗打格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275cc3072f1ac22f9ad2b93a744d95a856cb2615","tid":642791,"uid":62599,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:33:14.000Z","msg":"佢以前讀屎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現時就將喲屎讀出嚟"},{"pid":"053f866346244d1edcfc854204bc8f97dff65883","tid":642791,"uid":9732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:37:22.000Z","msg":"咁而家香港都叫中佔時期啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"774ad6c92d51d9a8c7b90f949815c9eeaee03b5a","tid":642791,"uid":156130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fd640b02ad214e9f2428acc7679baf762c4851eb","tid":642791,"uid":142888,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"台灣就係一直爭議緊 ，究竟日本殖民管治時期嗰陣應該叫 日治時期 定 日佔時期 好，台灣大中華膠同國民黨傾向叫日佔時期，所以有好多爭議<br />\n<br />\n香港一直都唔在乎呢啲事，就連3年06個月嗰陣 都叫日治時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過睇嚟香港好快就進入台灣呢啲爭議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲啲TVB都會開始叫英佔時期，仲要幫香港旗打格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:39:01.000Z","msg":"咁講由日本變返英國管咁仲叫唔叫光復香港？<br />\n<br />\n我認為叫英治英佔，不如叫英屬香港。"},{"pid":"8a088947b7df4ec25670e549476d78f312224966","tid":642791,"uid":62409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"重申中國政府不承認3條不平等條約的立場<br />\n<br />\n笑左 你承唔承認關人撚事<br />\n而家呢份約係邊個同邊個簽? <br />\n你唔好走去隔離屋話唔承認人地結婚"},{"pid":"1702314dd7cb575ebf175a6ede412324d0978ca0","tid":642791,"uid":3241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"歷史上北京條約有三條<br />\n分別係中英 / 中法 / 中俄<br />\n<br />\n好了，五毛狗同志，為什麼中英果條就係所謂不平等條約，而中俄果條就一直持續到今日，小支支政府更在符拉迪沃斯托克設置領事館呢?"},{"pid":"384744d9dad300fe92b678868e7d2160b50ab7a1","tid":642791,"uid":63909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"053f866346244d1edcfc854204bc8f97dff65883","tid":642791,"uid":9732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:37:22.000Z","msg":"咁而家香港都叫中佔時期啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"呢個說法不存爭議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53420f98739e8d831193f61e795b6b7486434d9","tid":642791,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1702314dd7cb575ebf175a6ede412324d0978ca0","tid":642791,"uid":3241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"歷史上北京條約有三條<br />\n分別係中英 / 中法 / 中俄<br />\n<br />\n好了，五毛狗同志，為什麼中英果條就係所謂不平等條約，而中俄果條就一直持續到今日，小支支政府更在符拉迪沃斯托克設置領事館呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/135000_0b74a56689ef40e9e7e896271ee10d17.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F135000_0b74a56689ef40e9e7e896271ee10d17.png&h=c655842a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64b98c926ebb4fa519cccca5480620fb0b88d143","tid":642791,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:52:07.000Z","msg":"唔係被迫<br />\n係打輸仗割地賠款"},{"pid":"1b63efd32bc8196186d4dc4972b8d7a0f3eab1de","tid":642791,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d70e0918f1040c78949dfef286293f0cb6d47c76","tid":642791,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fbaf6d3a1f2d1e3876b187d0b5b2a1249a2ff21","tid":642791,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b727404a74f8baee875c56c62991612db851db57","tid":642791,"uid":35870,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:08:43.000Z","msg":"咁係咪即係話英國政府係非法佔領香港，咁講法當時英國政府所批出嘅地契根本無效，我建議將所有新界土地歸還新界原居民，所有港九土地歸還水上人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"咁都揾到位吹奏原居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就好睇喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b142fae036ff6034875a5a1623e928e090c799","tid":642791,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:15:04.000Z","msg":"中聯辦:<br />\n<br />\n1841年，鴉片戰爭中清政府戰敗，被迫簽訂《中英南京條約》，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港（時屬新安縣）正式淪為英國的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">殖民地</span></span></strong>。 1887年，葡萄牙誘逼清政府簽訂《中葡和好通商條約》，侵占澳門（時屬香山縣）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.locpg.gov.cn/yeganghezuo2/guangdonggaikuang/200801/t20080126_3032.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.locpg.gov.cn%2Fyeganghezuo2%2Fguangdonggaikuang%2F200801%2Ft20080126_3032.asp&d=2FAxEgbFnn6Qln%2BSqq5WhYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=8c82fbab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.locpg.gov.cn/yeganghezuo2/guangdonggaikuang/200801/t20080126_3032.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n外交部副部長張業<br />\n<br />\n1842年，清政府被迫同英國簽訂了《南京條約》，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">使香港淪為英國<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">殖民地</span></span></strong>，這是中國近代史上第一個不平等條約，也是中國一步步淪為半殖民地半封建社會的開端。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/wjb_673085/zygy_673101/zysx_673103/xgxw_673105/t1217081.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fweb%2Fwjb_673085%2Fzygy_673101%2Fzysx_673103%2Fxgxw_673105%2Ft1217081.shtml&d=2FAxEgbFnn6Qln%2BSqq5WhYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2c868d4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/wjb_673085/zygy_673101/zysx_673103/xgxw_673105/t1217081.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n國防部/新華社<br />\n１９９７年７月１日，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">被英國殖民統治１００多年的香港</span></strong>終於回到祖國懷抱，&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;偉大構想開始在香港落地生根。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mod.gov.cn/big5/jmsd/2017-06/29/content_4783955.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mod.gov.cn%2Fbig5%2Fjmsd%2F2017-06%2F29%2Fcontent_4783955.htm&d=2FAxEgbFnn6Qln%2BSqq5WhYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=31b0a829\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mod.gov.cn/big5/jmsd/2017-06/29/content_4783955.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n全国港澳研究会<br />\n在1949年以前，中國是一個半殖民地半封建的社會，資本主義在中國還處於萌芽發展狀態，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港做為殖民地社會</span></strong>和當時中國其它很多地方來比較，香港是落後的<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hmo.gd.gov.cn/zwgk/ztzl/gzyj/ygayj/201701/t20170118_442820.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hmo.gd.gov.cn%2Fzwgk%2Fztzl%2Fgzyj%2Fygayj%2F201701%2Ft20170118_442820.htm&d=2FAxEgbFnn6Qln%2BSqq5WhYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ec44b537\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hmo.gd.gov.cn/zwgk/ztzl/gzyj/ygayj/201701/t20170118_442820.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9355a30f2e4fb055be1895e68f9fcd65060a528c","tid":642791,"uid":76245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"將